{"tid":426675,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣對抗老屎忽？","createTime":"2017-10-06T21:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T06:39:13.000Z","uid":75232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"926aaccc580bc0d5dc9177e6e9e234e92b34ab12","tid":426675,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T21:18:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我啱啱升咗職做實驗室經理。同一層另一個實驗室嗰度有個做咗十幾年嘅實驗室經理。佢平時都幾好人，不過一到公事上佢就好撚麻煩。咩都唔同我講直接同我阿頭講，明明我有權力去處理件事架嘛，都要驚動我阿頭，搞到我好似好撚無能咁。<br />\n<br />\n另外，送過嚟啲包裹一句唔好意思睇唔到個名就同我開撚咗佢，一啲禮貌都無。<br />\n<br />\n仲有次佢想我哋科水去買件儀器，我哋話肯出四分之一佢就發晒爛渣咁話出四分之一不如唔好出，廢事第時你哋搬嗰陣點之點分。今次佢就豪俾我哋不過下次有嘢要買嘅時候我哋就要識做。<br />\n<br />\n應該點樣應對呢啲老屎忽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f7229b650c00ec24b8db7b7f366b9d8db23d32","tid":426675,"uid":120986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T22:40:54.000Z","msg":"辭職"},{"pid":"f557fe43bf54c5dd2e0ffce25f9f1486677ac93c","tid":426675,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"781233ce010770be4f09a8981a14bd474568f97c","tid":426675,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買公家儀器點會唔出公數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該budget問題<br />\n1team 一半"},{"pid":"d43c6b3f8e610c538f8373cbcd7c88ba7eb265a9","tid":426675,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3d9c92cbeb3e0e04c6fe9d9185f40c39fb31ee","tid":426675,"uid":75232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辭職</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦，我由technician開始做，做咗七年先升到做實驗室經理。為咗個老屎忽就辭職？我仲要供樓供車架..."},{"pid":"4cf902e0577c55e27c4d00b307c88f10b1dc4efe","tid":426675,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買公家儀器點會唔出公數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該budget問題<br />\n1team 一半</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n每個實驗室都係獨立budget, 有時候有啲共用嘅儀器就會每個實驗室夾返份。<br />\n<br />\n利申Academic research"},{"pid":"0d088c01390213209bd12e95d9c3a8b405ed96f4","tid":426675,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"搣佢屎忽"},{"pid":"c1224ef8edcf02529ae4c80a5c065cad41d2e521","tid":426675,"uid":124958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"依d咁小既事, 一個經理都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 點做大事呀?"},{"pid":"a12e78f1ddd5f232cf3c6e25c3afd4412a3acc47","tid":426675,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依d咁小既事, 一個經理都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 點做大事呀?</blockquote><br />\n重話經理[sosad得果七年經驗 講到未即係出面officer grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c846fb871adf46014cadf03c4578206bb1d6ace","tid":426675,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依d咁小既事, 一個經理都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 點做大事呀?</blockquote><br />\n重話經理[sosad得果七年經驗 講到未即係出面officer grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是咁的，大學實驗室個阿頭係叫Principal Investigator (PI), 對落就係幫佢管理個實驗室嘅lab manager (我), 再對落就係啲technician. Postdoc直接under PI唔到我管。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅職責除咗係做實驗之外就係同供應商打關係，買貨，總之就係個超級打雜加管家。<br />\n<br />\n你話我得嗰七年經驗，照咁睇閣下應該有好多經驗，做到好高級架喇。咁唔該你教下我點樣應付你丫？"}]}